<h3>Horse-back Riding</h3>

<p>Take a step back in time and experience the adventure and romance of cowboy country. Explore the scenic meadows and mountain grandeur of Colorado&rsquo;s high country from astride your trusty steed. You will travel on some of the same trails that have been used for thousands of years. Ute and Arapahoe Indians once crossed these mountain passes seeking elk and deer. Later came the mountain men, trappers and prospectors. All crossed the high country on horseback. Come on out and Ride the Rockies&ndash;trail rides, wagon rides, breakfast or dinner rides are all waiting for you.</p>

